  <brief_title>Immunogenicity and Safety of TNFa Kinoid in Rheumatoid Arthritis With Secondary Resistance to TNFa Antagonists</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II, Randomized, Double-blind, Controlled Study to Evaluate the Immune Responses, Safety and Clinical Efficacy of Three Doses of Neovacs' TNF-Kinoid in Adult Patients With Rheumatoid Arthritis Who Have Relapsed Despite Anti-TNFα Biological Therapy</official_title>
