  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this trial is to demonstrate that active immunization with anti-TNFα kinoid
      (TNF-K) is able to induce polyclonal anti-TNFα antibodies in RA patients who were previously
      treated with anti-TNFα mAb but have lost susceptibility to therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
